Rodimus had remained quiet as Mallice and Dragos argued. Once they both left he finally spoke.

Rodimus Prime: If any others think that I made a mistake you can tell me in turn. Right now we have more serious issues. I&#39;;; go speak with this Mallice right now.

Rodimus makes his way to Mallice&#39;s quarters. Rodimus couldn&#39;t quite place this bot. He seemed familiar like they had known one another in the past. Not necissarely close, but knew each other.

Roddy presses the button that would alert Mallice of someone at his door.

Rodimus Prime: Mallice, it&#39;s Rodimus...

